snippet.title: Deceit 2 - Exclusive Release Trailer | Black Summer 2023
snippet.description: Watch the new trailer for the social deduction horror game Deceit 2. The sequel to the multiplayer horror game Deceit, offers intense social deduction gameplay as players must determine who to trust in a group of suspicious players. Deceit 2 is launching on September 14 for PlayStation 5, Xbox Series S|X, and PC.
